You need the following libraries:

If you use macports: 
sudo port selfupdate
sudo port install cmake py27-numpy, py27-scipy, boost +python27, py27-pil

If you use apt: 
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install python2.7-dev python-scipy python-cairo libboost-python-dev libboost-system-dev
libboost-thread-dev cmake 

Then, do 

source env.sh
./build.py

And you should be set. Email/gchat to ecuzzillo@gmail.com for support. 


